</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/vNsEwQpPBJc" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/10/21/god-of-war-is-coming-to-pc-in-january/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=god-of-war-is-coming-to-pc-in-january</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>蘋果擦拭布被搶購一空，最快 12 月底有貨</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/P6xQuxhby1c/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harold]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 21 Oct 2021 08:17:21 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple Store]]></category><category><![CDATA[擦拭布]]></category><category><![CDATA[蘋果]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1066996</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>蘋果早前發布會宣布推出多項新產品，相信最為矚目的是搭載新 Apple M1 Pro 晶片或 Apple M1  [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>蘋果早前發布會宣布推出多項新產品，相信最為矚目的是搭載新 Apple M1 Pro 晶片或 Apple M1 Max 晶片的 14 吋和 16 吋 MacBook Pro，以及第 3 代 AirPods，但一眾果迷需等多幾日，10 月 26 日才正式公開發售。但在新 MacBook Pro 及 AirPods 推出前，同是蘋果產品擦拭布經已引起網民熱烈討論，更有網民冠以「信仰之布」的名號。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Screenshot-2021-10-21-at-12.11.34-PM.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1066998 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Screenshot-2021-10-21-at-12.11.34-PM-694x368.png" alt="" width="694" height="368" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Screenshot-2021-10-21-at-12.11.34-PM-694x368.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Screenshot-2021-10-21-at-12.11.34-PM-1280x679.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Screenshot-2021-10-21-at-12.11.34-PM-768x407.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Screenshot-2021-10-21-at-12.11.34-PM-1536x814.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Screenshot-2021-10-21-at-12.11.34-PM-2048x1086.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Screenshot-2021-10-21-at-12.11.34-PM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲蘋果新推出擦拭布，官方售價 HK$ 149</p><p>蘋果推出最新產品擦拭布，官方宣稱「擦拭布以柔軟而不會造成磨損的物料製成，讓你安全有效地清潔任何 Apple 顯示器，包括 nano-texture 玻璃。」像是為蘋果產品度身訂造，官方售價為 HK$ 149 元。有網民認為擦拭布與坊間其他同類產品沒太大分別，亦不解為何定價 HK$ 149 元，戲稱其為「信仰之布」，意指買擦拭布的人就是「真果迷」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1067003 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Screenshot-2021-10-21-at-12.44.04-PM-694x555.png" alt="" width="694" height="555" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Screenshot-2021-10-21-at-12.44.04-PM-694x555.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Screenshot-2021-10-21-at-12.44.04-PM-1125x900.png 1125w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Screenshot-2021-10-21-at-12.44.04-PM-768x614.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Screenshot-2021-10-21-at-12.44.04-PM-1536x1229.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Screenshot-2021-10-21-at-12.44.04-PM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲網民戲稱擦拭布為「信仰之布」（LIHKG 截圖）</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1067000 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/MM6F3-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/MM6F3-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/MM6F3-900x900.jpeg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/MM6F3-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/MM6F3-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/MM6F3.jpeg 1144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1067001 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/MM6F3_AV1-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/MM6F3_AV1-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/MM6F3_AV1-900x900.jpeg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/MM6F3_AV1-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/MM6F3_AV1-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/MM6F3_AV1.jpeg 1144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1066999 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/MM6F3_AV2-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/MM6F3_AV2-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/MM6F3_AV2-900x900.jpeg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/MM6F3_AV2-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/MM6F3_AV2-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/MM6F3_AV2.jpeg 1144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>雖然網民一面倒批評蘋果，但「口裏說不，身體卻很誠實」，擦拭布一早被搶購一空，官網顯示所有 Apple Store 已沒有現貨，訂購送貨都要等 10 至 12 個星期，即最快 12 月底才有貨，分分鐘要等到 2022 年先有得用，值不值得就真的見仁見智。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk-zh/shop/product/MM6F3FE/A/擦拭布?fnode=829355e4bf6119fab28a0df80af5d0fb7868c438d3991d9281721385a81dc9506febdff013d1adadcb692f647a0ae614e5223adbe102d322fbf6db70d93d9de2f27dfc97f0ccfbda53fca60686e26968a164e6df6366015c040a437c318eccab">蘋果官網</a></p><p>&#8212;</p><p>unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
